<br>
As for the RP considerations, I would run my blade through every single ogre, troll, lizzie, and inkie (except one who has walked a path of redemption in front of me) on this server or die trying if  i could.  I'd be up for the alignments coming back---i've played with them for 24 years now.  <br>
<br>
I have played this game only three weeks now &amp; have found a wonderful family in the Ring of the Light (where we do try to RP/keep IC).  <br>
<br>
Yeah-PLEASE limit the renge on shout and re-limit auction to towns!  PLEASE eliminate goober names.  Please don't ask me why i say &quot;/g If you invite that ogre/troll/inkie/lizzie i must leave you all.&quot;  Please don't ask me why i haven't PLed when there are other honestly new people asking me can you help me find (not finish) my quest?  Do you know where the (insert name here) is?<br>
Please don't laugh at me for buffing with my 2 feeble paladin buffs your (not evil) character as i run by just because i can--even if you are a 62nd season gnome encahnter with more power than i can imagine.  (I really wasn't trying to subtly ask you for anything--i wasn't headed for combat and didn't need the mana.)<br>
<br>
Please take the SoW and KEI spells out of the game.  i get tired of hearing people beg for them.  GRR.  and don't ask me for one.<br>
<br>
But if you are a good aligned race and interested in chatting or helping me help others, send me a tell, please.<br>
<br>
Darmaid Ostlersson<br>
Knight of 23(!) quests in the service of TRUTH<br>
very junior member of the Ring of the Light<br>
